# ============================================================================
# ✅ DO:
#   - Generate unique passwords for each service
#   - Use minimum 32 characters for passwords
#   - Rotate passwords every 90 days
#   - Use Docker Secrets in production
#   - Keep .env file permissions: chmod 600 .env
#   - Backup .env file encrypted only
#
